data.description: Prepare to be impressed and bring your pickiest buyers to view this meticulously maintained home in beautiful Talavera. Why wait on new construction. This home was just completed in 2020 and shows beautifully! Features include gorgeous 18 inch tile flooring, window treatments throughout, recessed lighting, expansive kitchen with a large granite top island bar for gathering, stainless steel kitchen appliances, diagonal laid tile backsplash, and crisp white cabinetry. The rear covered porch overlooks a serene pond for extra privacy and relaxation. The large indoor laundry room with shelving and a tub sink, leads directly into the 3-car garage. Welcome to the Centex Homes "Palm" model, offering a split plan with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and neutral paint throughout. The Talavera amenities include a resort sized heart shaped pool with a splash pad, tennis and basketball courts, community social events, sidewalks throughout, beautiful wooded views, and a playground for the kiddos. While this home does have a Spring Hill address you get the benefit of Land O Lakes Schools!   Book a preview through Showing Time today and let's work together for a win-win!
